         One of the better tricks I saw for this was parking pet at entrance, getting deep in Nurga/Droga, and summoning pet to your side and letting it kill it's way up.</P><P>However, I should point out this will no longer work anymore, nor will AFK experience.  No mobs will attack your *neutral con pet*.  Rather efficent way to elimiate afk experience, and give pet casters an increase at the same time, no?</P><P><i><b><font color=gold><font size=4>Dinomight Questaholic</b></font id=size4><BR>Master of the Lizard Dance on Test  {The Grove}</i></font id=gold><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
